Build tools automates the process of building an executable. This gives each developer the ability to build and run software on their machine. A build tool can automate the process of downloading and managing dependencies.

ANT stands for another neat tool.Ant is also a java based build tool.
Ant is a platform neutral and can handle platform specific properties.
Ant scripts uses plain xml.Ant comes with big list of predefined tasks.
Ant is flexible and doesnt impose any coding conventions or project structure. 
Ant doesnt has formal conventions so we need to provide information of the project structure in xml file
Ant is procedural we need to provide information about what to do and when to do through code,and we also 
need to provide order of sequence.
Properties are used to customize the build process are defined in a build file.